{"tid":2279319,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"尖沙咀藍店Harlan’s新娘房冇得鎖疑洩春光 婚宴期間食客亂入 餐廳拒道歉","createTime":"2020-11-09T16:45:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-10T06:00:53.000Z","uid":364068,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"24500fb2bd8686226f69df58255edc52f847990b","tid":2279319,"uid":364068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T16:45:09.000Z","msg":"尖沙嘴熱門擺酒場地Harlan&rsquo;s Bar and Restaurant被指新娘房趟門不設門鎖，新娘更衣時疑被窺探。上月於該處擺酒的陳小姐（化名）指，Harlan&rsquo;s新娘房的更衣間其中一面為一扇趟門，與毗鄰的餐廳相通，但不設門鎖。她和親友曾在視察場地及婚宴當日下午提醒職員要鎖上趟門，惟餐廳未有理會，結果婚宴當晚趟門被打開，「換完衫見到有個男人坐咗喺度」。事主擔心換衫過程被偷拍上網，已經報警處理。餐廳回應指，事件已交警方處理，不便評論。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201110/TSX2H7DVZ5GGPENZJYUG4TNVE4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201110%2FTSX2H7DVZ5GGPENZJYUG4TNVE4%2F&d=YlPq7SqekvAy96d0W8R9y60J0iXDlbDdnmyxhWT3nOs%3D&h=4719b948\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201110%2FTSX2H7DVZ5GGPENZJYUG4TNVE4%2F&h=6c061ea6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201110/TSX2H7DVZ5GGPENZJYUG4TNVE4/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Aing9qV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAing9qV.png&h=2508c27f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-LsPT_IYCmQ?t=1375\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-LsPT_IYCmQ%3Ft%3D1375&d=YlPq7SqekvAy96d0W8R9y60J0iXDlbDdnmyxhWT3nOs%3D&h=44d0c4e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-LsPT_IYCmQ?t=1375</a>"},{"pid":"c8f42ead3dc57e411b682d4ed1497ecebee6cf8e","tid":2279319,"uid":364068,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T16:45:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1EooPC8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1EooPC8.png&h=2f915b79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BiaeWh9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.